#: _versions/3.34/guides/deploying-to-google-cloud.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use Maven to build the application using `mvn clean package`, it will generate a single JAR that contains all the classes of your application including its dependencies."
msgstr "Utilize o Maven para compilar o aplicativo com o comando ` `mvn clean package` `; isso irá gerar um único arquivo JAR que contém todas as classes do seu aplicativo, incluindo suas dependências."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/deploying-to-google-cloud.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Finally, use `gcloud` to deploy your application as an App Engine service."
